text: Gail Gaeng (born 27 December 1992) is an American wheelchair basketball player. She won a gold medal at the 2016 Summer Paralympics. She played at the 2011 Women's U25 Wheelchair Basketball World Championship, 2014 Women's World Wheelchair Basketball Championship, and 2015 Parapan American Games. == References == Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Paralympic gold medalists for the United States Category:American wheelchair basketball players
